CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 25, 1960, pg. A19, reads: "Alpha Wives - Chairmen of committees for the recent Alpha Wives' 'Fantasy of Roses' and luncheon-bridge at the Gateway Plaza was the above group... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Two women wearing hats with flowers, possibly wives of Alpha fraternity members, standing in Gateway Plaza
